comments.body:
This works the same way as it does in iOS. "auto" makes the ScrollView fit the parent container.

Test:
{code}
var win = Ti.UI.createWindow({
	backgroundColor: 'white'
});

var scrollView = Ti.UI.createScrollView({
	backgroundColor: 'red',
	width: 'auto',
	height: 'auto'
})

win.add(scrollView);

win.open();
{code}
